// trigger site writes them all with memory_order_relaxed, then
// release-stores into g_iconPopTimer last; any reader (IconPopAnimThread,
// or CDDS_ITEMPOSTPAINT's own paint-time check) acquire-loads
// g_iconPopTimer first, so a nonzero read guarantees the relaxed writes
// above are visible.
